These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, salsa, ambient, house
4 different games are played: bridge, domino, monopoly, billiard
House: futuristic, wooden, colonial, modern
1. the colonial house is on the left of the person playing domino##1
2. the modern house is the person playing bridge##1
3. the fan ambient is on the far left##1
4. the fan r&b is on the far right##1
5. the person playing domino is between the colonial house and the fan salsa##2
6. the wooden house is the person playing monopoly##1
7. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre        | ambient | house  | salsa | r&b  |
| Game         | billiard    | domino  | bridge       | monopoly     |
| House   | colonial     | futuristic | modern       | wooden |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
City: boston, san-francisco, prague, miami
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, bellflower, daffodil, poppy
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, airplane, car, subway
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the van is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
3. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the subway is between the person who growspoppy and the person traveling to miami##2
5. the person who growspoppy is the person driving the airplane##1
6. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person driving the van##1
7. the person who growsdaffodil is the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| City         | san-francisco | boston    | miami  | prague |
| Flower   | poppy  | begonia  | bellflower   | daffodil    |
| Transport         | airplane | subway | van | car      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, goat, ferret, dog
4 different games are played: domino, canasta, monopoly, backgammon
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, bellflower, orchid, zinnia
1. the person who growsbellflower is between the person who growszinnia and the owner of the goat##2
2. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1
5. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
6. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
7. the person who growsorchid is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Pet      | goat | dog         | lizard   | ferret    |
| Game         | canasta | backgammon | domino | monopoly |
| Flower   | orchid   | bellflower        | zinnia      | begonia   |

