.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-4::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, watermelon, cucumber, peach
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, october, july, april
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, oliveros, alhambra, bongani
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the davidoff-smoker is between the bongani-smoker and the person eating peach##2
3. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
6. the bongani-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in february and the oliveros-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Food   | peach        | watermelon   | tomato | cucumber |
| Birthday         | july | february | october    | april |
| Cigar     | alhambra       | davidoff     | bongani       | oliveros    |

