.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
City: marseilles, san-francisco, liverpool, edinburgh
House: futuristic, victorian, gothic-revival, modern
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, car, scooter, bike
1. the person driving the bike is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
2. the person driving the bike is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the gothic-revival house is on the far right##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
6. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the victorian house##1
7. the person driving the bike is between the person driving the scooter and the futuristic house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| City   | marseilles | edinburgh      | san-francisco       | liverpool   |
| House      | futuristic   | victorian  | modern | gothic-revival     |
| Transport      | car     | bike | scooter        | jet-ski |

