.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, taxi, bus, boat
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, gospel, house, indie
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, teacher, dressmaker, security-guard
1. the fan indie is on the left of the teacher##1
2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the dressmaker##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the police-officer##1
4. the security-guard is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
5. the fan jazz is between the fan indie and the dressmaker##2
6. the person driving the taxi is between the person driving the bike and the person driving the bus##2
7. the police-officer is on the right of the fan house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Transport    | bus | taxi  | bike | boat      |
| Music-Genre   | house  | indie  | jazz | gospel |
| Job   | security-guard | police-officer | teacher | dressmaker     |

