.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, hamster, frog, dog
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, 7up, soy-milk, fanta
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, car, bike, trike
1. the person driving the trike is the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person driving the bike is the person drinking tea##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
6. the owner of the hamster is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking soy-milk##2
7. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Pet          | frog  | hamster    | dog | goldfish  |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | fanta       | 7up        | tea    |
| Transport         | car | ship | trike  | bike |

