.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, apple, pear, lemon
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, skateboarding, snowboarding, tennis
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, balloon-flower, orchid, daffodil
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person eating apple##2
3. the person eating pear is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
4. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
6. the person eating pear is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Food         | lemon  | apple | pear | peas |
| Sport   | weightlifting  | tennis | skateboarding   | snowboarding         |
| Flower           | marigold | orchid  | balloon-flower   | daffodil      |

