.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
4 different games are played: billiard, backgammon, domino, monopoly
House: craftsman, farmhouse, palace, colonial
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, white, azure, blood-red
1. the person who likes azure is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
2. the farmhouse house is the person playing billiard##1
3. the person who likes white is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the palace house is the person playing backgammon##1
5. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
6. the palace house is on the far right##1
7. the farmhouse house is between the person who likes azure and the craftsman house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Game          | monopoly  | billiard    | domino | backgammon       |
| House         | colonial | farmhouse | craftsman  | palace |
| Color   | azure   | blood-red      | white  | orange     |

