4 different pets are kept: goat, rabbit, chinchilla, pony
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, russian, malaysian, indonesian
1. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
2. the victorian house is on the far left##1
3. the cape-cod house is between the wooden house and the owner of the rabbit##2
4. the russian is on the right of the palace house##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
6. the russian is on the right of the palace house##1
7. the indonesian is the owner of the pony##1
8. the chinese is the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| House          | victorian      | palace | cape-cod | wooden |
| Pet         | pony   | rabbit  | goat | chinchilla |
| Nationality   | indonesian | chinese   | russian | malaysian |

