.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, 7up, soy-milk, milk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, september, august, march
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, ivory, azure, lilac
1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the person who likes azure is the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person who likes green is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in august##2
4. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who likes green and the person drinking milk##2
5. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who likes lilac##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who likes ivory##1
7. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage    | milk  | soy-milk | water | 7up     |
| Birthday   | november | august   | march  | september    |
| Color     | ivory        | lilac       | green      | azure |

