.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, havana, game, bluemaster
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, documentary, crime, zombie
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, march, february, november
1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is the game-smoker##1
3. the havana-smoker is between the game-smoker and the person watching documentary movies##2
4. the person watching crime movies is on the far left##1
5. the havana-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far right##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | game     | havana | baccarat       |
| Movie-Genre      | crime  | zombie | adventure  | documentary |
| Birthday        | november  | march      | february        | january      |

