3. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person eating peach##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
5. the tower house is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person eating mango##2
6. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1
7. the tower house is the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
