.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, june, october, august
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, american, thai, italian
House: cape-cod, farmhouse, gothic-revival, art-deco
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1
2. the thai is between the person who's birthday is in august and the gothic-revival house##2
3. the art-deco house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
4. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1
5. the pakistani is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
6. the american is on the right of the thai##1
7. the person who's birthday is in october is the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Birthday   | april    | june | august           | october |
| Nationality       | pakistani | thai    | american          | italian   |
| House      | gothic-revival  | farmhouse   | art-deco | cape-cod  |

