.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, rock-climbing, photography, sudoku
4 different games are played: billiard, mah-jongg, canasta, backgammon
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, chinese, indian, pakistani
1. the person playing canasta is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the canadian##1
3. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person playing canasta and the person playing billiard##2
5. the chinese is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the pakistani is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the canadian##2
7. the person playing backgammon is the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Hobby      | photography | hiking | rock-climbing     | sudoku   |
| Game   | billiard | backgammon        | canasta  | mah-jongg  |
| Nationality           | canadian      | pakistani         | chinese | indian |

