.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, january, november, may
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, almond-milk, water, sprite
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: trance, d&b, jazz, r&b
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the fan d&b is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
5. the fan r&b is the person drinking sprite##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person who's birthday is in may and the fan jazz##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday        | may | january | september | november |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate       | almond-milk     | water   | sprite   |
| Music-Genre   | trance | d&b | jazz | r&b |

 